title: Beautiful Home For Rent (Beautiful Neighborhood)
posting_body: QR Code Link to This Post   This is a Trilevel Home. It was built in 2004. The subdivision is Tiburon, which is in the Schererville, IN area. It has 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, a Living Room, a Dining Room, a Kitchen, a Family Room, and a Laundry Room. It has a 2 1/2 car garage connected to the home. It has a big front and backyard. It has a deck.  The appliances that are included with the home are:  Refrigerator, Microwave, Stove, Dishwasher, and Blinds  No pets  Available: Saturday June 25, 2022  Please call: Steve & Suzy (219) 743-1224
